{"tid":776437,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"碧基退出西班牙國家隊","createTime":"2018-08-12T05:46:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-12T06:51:03.000Z","uid":147522,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2e3fbb82bd3eb2b7003dadf829f044c0cbeb19e0","tid":776437,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T05:46:30.000Z","msg":"中堅碧基周六宣佈退出西班牙國家隊。<br />\n<br />\n「我有過美好時光，贏得歐國盃及世界盃，但故事終於要完結。」31歲的碧基（Gerard Pique）在2009年初次入選西班牙，至今已上陣102場攻入5球，如今選擇退役。「我已告訴教練安歷基。在世界盃後離開，合情合理。」<br />\n<br />\n碧基今夏助西班牙出戰世界盃，於16強不敵主辦國俄羅斯，他續表示：「那是一段快樂的時間，我經歷過很好神奇的事實，但有時候，你要在合適的時候，終止一個循環。」<br />\n<br />\n早前，在加泰羅尼亞出生的碧基，因為支持加泰羅尼亞獨立，被西班牙球迷聲討，更在於比賽及操練期間被喝倒彩。另外，亦有傳效力巴塞隆拿的他，跟國家隊中堅拍檔、效力宿敵皇家馬德里的沙治奧拉莫斯不和。"},{"pid":"2f547996d81c44e15444bc224b368c5f355b7b1e","tid":776437,"uid":59283,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T05:47:52.000Z","msg":"最後一場一個手球害死西班牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c536e9a7204795b32741cb6cbc14864e38407ab","tid":776437,"uid":52006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2f547996d81c44e15444bc224b368c5f355b7b1e","tid":776437,"uid":59283,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T05:47:52.000Z","msg":"最後一場一個手球害死西班牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T05:55:14.000Z","msg":"Catalonia is not Spain<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9aa6ffe13368a6afa447e2022e1c0d55559a9c2","tid":776437,"uid":29993,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f547996d81c44e15444bc224b368c5f355b7b1e","tid":776437,"uid":59283,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T05:47:52.000Z","msg":"最後一場一個手球害死西班牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T05:56:54.000Z","msg":"最後一場係對俄仔加時輸12碼喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"682be14b6c7ad574c8f80088f780e46fc2f